headline.main: Republicans Join Democratic Call for Clarity on Trump Abortion Order
headline.print_headline: Republicans Join Democratic Call for Clarity on Trump Abortion Order

lead_paragraph: Two of President Donald Trump's fellow Republicans joined four Democrats on Monday in demanding that the White House provide more information about an executive order that has sown confusion among international organizations involved in family planning, AIDS treatment and other healthcare issues.
